overview:
Xpress Restoration offers 24/7 Emergency Services for Water Damage, Fire Damage and Mold Damage Emergencies in San Diego, Chula Vista, National City, Lemon Grove, La Mesa and Spring Valley, CA. Xpress Restoration specialize in restoring properties in restoring and remodeling residential or commercial properties. Our emergency restoration services include water damage restoration, sewage removal, fire damage restoration, mold removal, flood water extraction, flooring and floor cleaning, carpet cleaning, kitchen and bath remodeling.

At Xpress Restoration Inc., our customer’s satisfaction is our priority, our staff will always strive to meet and exceed your expectations. For this reason, we are your go to company for all your insurance restoration and remodeling needs.
